Impressive.

31
00:02:11,710 --> 00:02:13,120
Zeyu, you’re indeed a genius.

32
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:13,960
Well done.

33
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:14,910
That’s flattering.

34
00:02:14,910 --> 00:02:15,840
