you can message me on this app.

44
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:42,150
When you message me,

45
00:02:42,470 --> 00:02:43,360
I’ll definitely reply.

46
00:02:44,310 --> 00:02:45,150
Moreover,

47
00:02:46,150 --> 00:02:47,910
I wish you to be
the first user of this app.

48
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:52,070
Okay.

49
00:02:52,470 --> 00:02:53,280
I accept it,

50
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,430
but as your classmate.

51
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:58,840
Can you

52
