Yes, I do.

54
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:07,870
Go back.

55
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,000
I’ll go now.

56
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:09,630
I’ll go too.

57
00:03:10,510 --> 00:03:11,300
-Bye-bye.
-Bye-bye.

58
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:31,470
We’ll do the transfer procedures
the day after tomorrow.

59
00:03:32,310 --> 00:03:33,470
Don’t blame me.

60
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,000
It’s for your own good.

61
00:03:38,310 --> 00:03:39,590
Yes, I know.

62
00:03:41,470 --> 00:03:42,150
Zeyu,

63
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:44,960
if you don’t want to get transferred,

64
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,710
just tell mom and dad.

65
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:53,910
It’s fine.

66
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:55,590
I have no objection.

67
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:09,150
Zeyu, may I come in?

68
00:04:09,750 --> 00:04:10,630
Come in, dad.

69
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:16,950
Have some water.

70
00:04:16,950 --> 00:04:17,680
Thanks.

71
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:21,600
Dad, what’s the matter?

72
00:04:22,310 --> 00:04:23,870
Oh. Sit down.

73
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,070
Zeyu,

74
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,310
you can just tell us

75
00:04:34,950 --> 00:04:36,040
what’s on your mind.

76
00:04:38,390 --> 00:04:39,190
