77
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,720
our family’s education

78
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:42,040
is a bit too stern.

79
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:45,270
Dad, you usually talk
when we’re having dinner.

80
00:04:45,830 --> 00:04:46,680
I can’t

81
00:04:47,310 --> 00:04:48,390
eat a meal properly.

82
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:50,680
Now, you suddenly came to my room.

83
00:04:51,390 --> 00:04:52,480
I’m not used to this.

84
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,270
Are you

85
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:58,040
mad at me?

86
00:04:59,310 --> 00:05:00,390
I know you want what’s the best for me.

87
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:01,720
Thanks, dad.

88
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:03,680
I’ll report to the new school
the day after tomorrow.

89
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,510
I want to go to bed now.

90
00:05:05,510 --> 00:05:06,240
Oh.

91
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,070
Then...

92
00:05:09,270 --> 00:05:09,800
Fine.

93
00:05:35,580 --> 00:05:37,140
(Qi Bangwei, Hematology Department,
Wanhe Hospital, Haiwen)

94
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,240
Caixi’s

95
00:05:44,070 --> 00:05:45,390
hemoglobin concentration

96
00:05:45,390 --> 00:05:47,600
is 65 grams per liter.

97
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:48,510
She has

98
00:05:48,510 --> 00:05:50,190
moderate anemia.

99
00:05:50,190 --> 00:05:52,560
The average size of
her red blood cell is small

100
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:54,510
and her hemoglobin level

101
00:05:54,510 --> 00:05:56,040
is low.

102
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:57,800
What does that mean?

103
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,480
It means that

104
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,270
your sister,

105
00:06:01,750 --> 00:06:02,630
Caixi,

106
00:06:02,630 --> 00:06:04,360
has iron deficiency anemia,

107
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:05,600
not leukemia.

108
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,000
Caixi.

109
00:06:07,630 --> 00:06:08,800
You’re not ill.

110
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,190
-Thank you, Dr. Qi.
-I’m not...

111
00:06:10,190 --> 00:06:11,120
No, I’m a little ill.

112
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,160
It’s not leukemia.

113
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:15,680
Yuan Haoxi, it’s iron deficiency anemia.

114
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:18,070
-I was so scared.
-I was so freaked out.

115
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:29,800
Yuan Caixi.

116
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,630
I’m warning you.

117
00:06:33,630 --> 00:06:35,680
From now on, when you feel sick,

118
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:37,120
you must tell me.

119
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,390
Bear it in mind, okay?

120
00:06:38,390 --> 00:06:39,270
Okay.

121
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,950
Thank the doctor.

122
00:06:44,950 --> 00:06:46,000
Doctor Qi.

123
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,160
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

124
00:06:50,310 --> 00:06:51,600
In this case,

125
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:53,000
you can rest assured.

126
00:06:54,160 --> 00:06:55,070
Caixi,

127
00:06:55,070 --> 00:06:56,390
although it’s a false alarm,

128
00:06:56,390 --> 00:06:59,070
this is your body’s
warning sign for you.

129
00:06:59,070 --> 00:07:01,510
I know College Entrance Exam is close.

130
00:07:01,950 --> 00:07:04,120
But you have to take enough rest.

131
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:05,190
Take care of your health.

132
00:07:05,190 --> 00:07:07,240
-Okay. I get it.
-Do you get it?

133
00:07:07,830 --> 00:07:08,600
Thank you, Dr. Qi.

134
00:07:09,310 --> 00:07:10,870
I guess we should be leaving.

135
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:11,630
Okay.

136
00:07:11,630 --> 00:07:12,310
Thank you, Dr. Qi.

137
00:07:12,310 --> 00:07:12,800
Thank you.

138
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:14,000
-Take care.
-Bye, Dr. Qi.

139
00:07:15,270 --> 00:07:15,780
Let’s go.

140
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:16,870
It’s time.

141
00:07:17,750 --> 00:07:18,260
Something got into your eyes?

142
00:07:18,260 --> 00:07:19,600
Listen! I’m so strong right now.

143
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,430
You’re so annoying.

144
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:31,600
Look at this.

145
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:34,070
