146
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:35,870
Like me?

147
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:40,390
Yuan!

148
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:44,000
Yuan, you’re back!

149
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:45,360
Han Yayi.

150
00:07:46,270 --> 00:07:47,800
That’s enough. That’s enough.

151
00:07:55,830 --> 00:07:56,950
