159
00:08:05,950 --> 00:08:07,600
You won’t hold a grudge
against us, right?

160
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:09,070
Now, you’re fine.

161
00:08:09,070 --> 00:08:10,160
Chief can stop worrying.

162
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:11,680
We can have a better time now.

163
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:12,360
Yes.

164
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:13,750
What?

165
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,160
You had a rough time before?

166
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,390
Maybe they did.

167
00:08:19,830 --> 00:08:20,390
Li He.

168
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:21,800
Ay.

169
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:26,560
Caixi.

170
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:29,360
Has the result come out?

171
00:08:29,750 --> 00:08:30,310
How is it?

172
00:08:33,270 --> 00:08:34,440
It’s such an important matter.

173
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,750
I was supposed to
tell the class teacher.

174
00:08:36,670 --> 00:08:37,240
Miss Luo.

175
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:37,750
I’m sorry for

176
00:08:37,750 --> 00:08:38,600
making you worry.

177
00:08:38,790 --> 00:08:39,480
I’m fine.

178
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,510
It’s just average anemia.

179
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:43,790
It’s great that you’re fine.

180
00:08:44,510 --> 00:08:45,320
Silly kid.

181
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:46,840
Thank you, Miss Luo.

182
00:08:48,030 --> 00:08:48,720
It’s great that you’re fine.

183
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:51,030
Han Yayi.

184
00:08:55,270 --> 00:08:55,910
Wait.

185
00:08:55,910 --> 00:08:56,790
Why is Zeyu absent?

186
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:58,030
He asked for a leave.

187
00:08:58,510 --> 00:08:59,240
A leave?

188
00:09:00,670 --> 00:09:02,030
He seems to have caught a cold.

189
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:03,440
Or,

190
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,150
something happened in his family.

191
00:09:17,390 --> 00:09:18,030
Brothers.

192
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,480
I’m in the race.

193
00:09:22,790 --> 00:09:23,790
Someone got hurt and quit the game.

194
00:09:23,790 --> 00:09:24,600
The one ranking behind him
will substitute for him.

195
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:25,870
So,

196
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,550
I can compete in the final next week.

197
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:38,630
Chief, I know you can do it.

198
00:09:38,630 --> 00:09:39,720
Well done, Chief.

199
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:42,670
It’s time to take back

200
00:09:42,670 --> 00:09:43,670
