201
00:09:43,670 --> 00:09:44,550
I must take it back.

202
00:09:46,030 --> 00:09:47,080
It’s good to be young.

203
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,200
Will you come next week?

204
00:09:50,870 --> 00:09:51,440
Of course.

205
00:09:51,910 --> 00:09:52,750
But this time,

206
00:09:52,750 --> 00:09:53,910
you have no reason to lose.

207
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,630
The process of hard work
matters the most.

208
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:57,960
Don’t worry.

209
00:09:58,600 --> 00:09:59,320
As long as you’re there,

210
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:01,000
I can definitely win.

211
00:10:03,870 --> 00:10:04,840
It’s time for class.

212
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:06,000
Go back.

213
00:10:14,870 --> 00:10:15,550
