225
00:11:30,670 --> 00:11:31,670
I saw him.

226
00:11:31,670 --> 00:11:33,080
But he went elsewhere.

227
00:11:33,910 --> 00:11:34,790
Elsewhere?

228
00:11:35,270 --> 00:11:36,120
He didn’t come here with you?

229
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:37,000
No.

230
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:38,240
And seems that there’s
something on his mind.

231
00:11:42,860 --> 00:11:44,820
(Zeyu
Where are you?)

232
00:11:45,750 --> 00:11:46,750
