233
00:11:46,910 --> 00:11:47,630
But he didn’t reply.

234
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:48,910
Did he reply to you?

235
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:49,750
No.

236
00:11:50,510 --> 00:11:51,320
What’s going on with him recently?

237
00:11:52,750 --> 00:11:53,600
I don’t know.

238
00:11:55,980 --> 00:11:57,060
(Ning Zeyu)

239
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:58,870
What is this app?

240
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:00,910
Zeyu installed it for me last time.

241
00:12:00,910 --> 00:12:02,790
He said I could contact him on it.

242
00:12:04,870 --> 00:12:05,550
Oh.

243
00:12:14,940 --> 00:12:17,780
(You have 3 new messages)

244
00:12:20,220 --> 00:12:23,580
(Yuan Caixi)

245
00:12:33,790 --> 00:12:35,150
No one should miss out.

246
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:46,750
Seems that you need to get used to that.

247
00:12:47,270 --> 00:12:48,870
My mom has already decided to
transfer me to another school.

248
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:52,480
Tomorrow, I’ll report to
No. 2 Experimental Middle School.

249
00:12:57,890 --> 00:13:02,050
♪Looking at you through the space
between my fingers♪

250
00:13:05,570 --> 00:13:10,010
♪How lucky I am to be occupied by you♪

251
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:16,560
♪My whole world My whole sight♪

252
00:13:16,560 --> 00:13:20,480
♪Hold the joy of youth in my palms♪

253
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:25,220
♪The gentleness of scattering stars♪

254
00:13:26,540 --> 00:13:29,420
(Yuan Caixi)

255
00:13:29,420 --> 00:13:32,570
♪Luckily I once met you♪

256
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:33,440
Seems that

257
00:13:34,750 --> 00:13:36,550
it’s not a big deal that one misses out.

258
00:13:37,270 --> 00:13:41,590
♪Blinked at a light year away♪

259
00:13:44,210 --> 00:13:51,040
♪The faint radiance is gradually fading♪

260
00:13:52,130 --> 00:13:59,090
♪Is this my illusion♪

261
00:13:59,930 --> 00:14:05,600
♪Not every wish needs to come true♪

262
00:14:07,650 --> 00:14:14,920
♪Stars shine and fade away♪

263
00:14:15,590 --> 00:14:22,860
♪I don’t want to go to bed
Tonight’s sky is full of drifting clouds♪

264
00:14:23,420 --> 00:14:29,110
♪The nights I spent missing you
are so precious♪

265
00:14:56,150 --> 00:14:58,080
I’ll handle the transfer procedures
with your dad.

266
00:14:58,080 --> 00:14:58,960
Sort out your stuff

267
00:14:58,960 --> 00:15:00,080
and come here fast.

268
00:15:00,510 --> 00:15:01,200
Okay.

269
00:15:01,750 --> 00:15:02,600
There won’t be

270
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:04,910
