271
00:15:04,910 --> 00:15:06,240
You can focus on your study.

272
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:08,360
Come home early

273
00:15:08,360 --> 00:15:09,550
after school.

274
00:15:10,630 --> 00:15:11,720
If you have any questions,

275
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:13,000
you can turn to online courses.

276
00:15:14,840 --> 00:15:15,960
Zeyu!

277
00:15:16,670 --> 00:15:18,240
Zeyu, look here!

